23
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:11,865
I guess you didn't miss me at all.

24
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:56,309
Check if it's good,</i>
then write up a quick piece and post it.</i>

25
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:01,581
SUNGWOO DAILY

26
